I have become aware that I do not have a normal version of Keen 6; the 1.4 to 1.0 and 1.0 to 1.4 programs list it as 'unknown version' The program itself lists itself as Version 1.13.

Also it comes with version 1.4 EGAHEAD and GAMEMAPS files, and also a lot of files ending with .RSH, .LBM and .HUF, without which the game becomes very difficult to play.

Does anyone have any idea what version I have, or could anyone mail me the 1.4 Keen6.EXE?A proud member of the signature stealing society
